snippet.title: Haunted Lands Gameplay
snippet.description:
DOS style action platformer, homage to classic games, such as Dangerous Dave and Doom.
Blast your way through the hordes of ghouls and demons, leaving behind nothing but their rotting corpses.

Play now for free:
https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/740700
or
https://alevgor.itch.io/haunted-lands
Music theme:
https://www.newgrounds.com/audio/listen/686619
